self-as for me I am not strong but am very content and happy, Lulu and her boys drove down from Minneapolis last Summer, I correspond with Mr. Bailey and Bardwell - He has been so nice to write, I Enjoy his letters and I feel as tho I had heard from <unclear/> the weather is turning much colder this morning. - They are still pulling turnups out of my garden down home I suppose this that will soon End Dearest girl this letter carries loads of love to you and all of yours, Had cards from Miss "Fish" & Miss "Knapp" 
